00:01:42,850 --> 00:01:44,320
I'm heading out.

2
00:01:47,530 --> 00:01:49,420
Ah, bocchan, good morning!

3
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,480
Shoveling the snow...

4
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:54,940
Good morning.

5
00:01:55,230 --> 00:01:56,530
You don't have to.

6
00:02:00,610 --> 00:02:04,380
Since I'm not going to school, my body's been too idle.

7
00:02:04,990 --> 00:02:06,980
So this is like a substitute for club activities.

8
00:02:07,010 --> 00:02:08,030
I see...

9
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:10,540
Be careful.

10
